# Icon Library Preference

**ALWAYS use Hugeicons instead of lucide-react for icons in this project.**

## Import Pattern

```typescript
import { IconName } from "@hugeicons/core-free-icons";
import { HugeiconsIcon } from "@hugeicons/react";
```

## Usage Pattern

```typescript
<HugeiconsIcon
  icon={IconName}
  size={16}
  color="currentColor"
  strokeWidth={2}
/>
```

## Notes

- Never import from `lucide-react`
- Always use the `HugeiconsIcon` wrapper component from `@hugeicons/react`
- Import icon definitions from `@hugeicons/core-free-icons`
- Common icon names follow patterns like `Cancel01Icon`, `Close01Icon`, `CheckmarkCircle02Icon`, etc.
